window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Magic is stirring, bloodlines are awakening, and the farm has never been more fertile!</p> <p>Life at Lucky Nickel Acres has reached a chaotic new normal. Ben's first litter of demi-beast babies are growing at an alarming rate, Citrine the Harpy Queen is frantically preparing to lay her royal egg, and Lady Helena Graythorne—once Ben's sworn enemy—is secretly working to topple Cinderfell's corrupt leadership from within.</p> <p>But beneath the bustling farm, ancient secrets lie dormant. When strange dreams connect Ben to the legendary Grand Vizier, he discovers a hidden door in the cellar that might hold the key to his mysterious powers and growing strength.</p> <p>As Ben and his mates work to establish their sanctuary as a proper Greenhold, their rapidly developing children begin to manifest abilities not seen in generations. The land itself seems to be responding to their magic, with plants growing more vibrant, animals showing unusual intelligence, and even the turkeys plotting what can only be rebellion.</p> <p>With his Master Breeder status unlocked and the bunny sisters eagerly awaiting their turn in his bed, Ben's virility has never been stronger. But as dormant bloodlines awaken and forgotten powers resurface, Lucky Nickel Acres becomes more than just a haven for demi-beasts—it's becoming the epicenter of a magical renaissance that could reshape all of Faerowilde.</p> <p>When the hidden forces of Cinderfell threaten everything they've built, Ben and his extraordinary family must harness their newfound abilities to protect their flourishing paradise. After all, a farm this fertile is absolutely worth fighting for!</p>"; 
